OL,3,CFishermen recall mystery of 'yellow
OL,4,Csubmarine' hauled ashore on Islay in
OL,5,C2005
OL,7,FTwo fishermen have recalled how they
OL,8,Funexpectedly hauled in a "yellow
OL,9,Fsubmarine" off Islay more than 20
OL,10,Fyears ago, with their surprising catch
OL,11,Fprompting a months-long mystery.
OL,13,FJohn Baker, now 69, was working a few
OL,14,Fmiles off the coast of the Inner
OL,15,FHebrides island when he came across
OL,16,Fthe strange vessel in May 2005.
OL,18,FHe reeled in the 10ft craft, which
OL,19,Fweighed around 850kg.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@JO]
