OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780275788
OL,3,CFishermen recall mystery of 'yellow
OL,4,Csubmarine' hauled ashore on Islay in
OL,5,C2005
OL,7,FIn a video recorded for the
OL,8,Fdistillery, Mr Baker said he initially
OL,9,Fthought the craft was some kind of
OL,10,Fbuoy when he spotted it in the water,
OL,11,Fbefore realising it was "something
OL,12,Fsignificant".
OL,14,FHe said: "There was no way of getting
OL,15,Fit aboard, so we got a rope on it and
OL,16,Fstarted towing it.
OL,18,F"The weather wasn't helping ` it was
OL,19,Fhard going ` but we knew we had to get
OL,20,Fit ashore and figure out what it was.
OL,26,@sD@YOUtD@LO]vD@JOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
