PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780275788
OL,3,CFishermen recall mystery of 'yellow
OL,4,Csubmarine' hauled ashore on Islay in
OL,5,C2005
OL,7,F"We knew it was some kind of
OL,8,Fsubmersible, but we had no idea where
OL,9,Fit had come from."
OL,11,FThe Ministry of Defence initially
OL,12,Fdenied it owned the submersible, but
OL,13,Fwhen the fishermen were able to
OL,14,Fprovide serial numbers the official
OL,15,Fstory changed.
OL,17,FMr Hastie, now 72, reflected on the
OL,18,Finternational attention created by the
OL,19,Fmystery.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
