CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780275788
OL,3,CFishermen recall mystery of 'yellow
OL,4,Csubmarine' hauled ashore on Islay in
OL,5,C2005
OL,7,FHe said: "It just grew arms and legs.
OL,8,FWhat started as a local curiosity
OL,9,Fbecame something people were talking
OL,10,Fabout all over the world.
OL,12,F"One minute it's sitting there in Port
OL,13,FEllen, the next we're doing interviews
OL,14,Fwith everyone ` every newspaper in
OL,15,FBritain, BBC World Service, even calls
OL,16,Ffrom overseas.
OL,18,F"It just went mad."
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUzD@AOUzD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
