OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780275788
OL,3,CFishermen recall mystery of 'yellow
OL,4,Csubmarine' hauled ashore on Islay in
OL,5,C2005
OL,7,FMr Baker became something of a local
OL,8,Fcelebrity after his discovery of the
OL,9,Fcraft.
OL,11,FHe said: ""I didn't buy a dram for
OL,12,Fthree months.
OL,14,F"Everywhere you went, people wanted to
OL,15,Fhear about it."
OL,17,FWhile the "yellow submarine" was still
OL,18,Fon the island, Bruichladdich quickly
OL,19,Fcreated a whisky named after the
OL,20,Fstrange vessel.
OL,26,@sD@JOUsD@KOUvD@AOUwD@OO]yD@KOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
