OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780275788
OL,3,CFishermen recall mystery of 'yellow
OL,4,Csubmarine' hauled ashore on Islay in
OL,5,C2005
OL,7,FThe distillery is now releasing a new
OL,8,F14-year-old limited edition single
OL,9,Fmalt of its Yellow Submarine whisky.
OL,11,FIn 2018, Bruichladdich acquired and
OL,12,Frestored a replica version of the
OL,13,Fsubmersible.
OL,15,FIt now stands in the distillery
OL,16,Fcourtyard as a permanent reminder of
OL,17,Fthe episode.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
